<br>
Like I said the turn out was Huge, had 9 full groups, big over kill. But was fun.<br>
<br>
Congrat going out to all that won on drops :<br>
Vonalbrecht got Ravultant Whip<br>
Wizra got Apothic Robe<br>
Donatelo got Scaled hierophant Breastplate and Vambraces<br>
Fantastha got Etherreal Mist Chestplate<br>
Sapp won Trueheart Sheild<br>
Healdra won Ethereal Mist Greaves and boots<br>
<br>
there was more dropped but by time time i knew i had to write thing down i tried going back and getting it all<br>
<br>
A really big congrat go to Xbit for Eye of Innoruuk and Tarnas for Hand of the Maestro both get pieces for there epic.<br>
<br>
I learned that I need alot more pratices on setting up group and running raid and I turned the Hate raid over to Destrie.<br>
<br>
I did watch the way he ran things, I did watch that alot of people didn't listen. I told out of all we had 10 deaths. <br>
<br>
Thank you again for coming. I will try to post more when it comes to mind.<br>
<br>
Lovbug Diesaton<br>
Proud officer of Blood and Iron<br>
